    "en": {
      "name": "Primoredial Schiller",
      "effect": "Reveal 1 Normal Monster or \"Primoredial\" card in your hand, except \"Primoredial Schiller\", then target 1 face-up card on the field (if you control a Normal Monster or a Level 5 or higher \"Primoredial\" monster, except a Token, you do not have to reveal a card); negate its effects, and if you do, banish it. During your Main Phase, if you control a \"Primoredial\" monster: You can Set this card from your GY. You can only use each effect of \"Primoredial Schiller\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
